          "🔎 Understand\n-------------\n\n> Secure coding principles shall be applied to software development.\n> \n> **_ISO® 27001_**\n\nSecure coding combines organization-wide standards and secure development practices to ensure software security. Also, continuous testing and regular updates are essential to identify vulnerabilities and protect against emerging threats.\n\n\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\n\n✅ Implement\n-----------\n\n**We provided some documents for you that you can find in the documents area of Cybermap:**\n\n*   [Software Development policy](https://cybermap.circle.so/c/all-documents/software-development-policy)\n    \n\n**Make sure to implement as follows:**\n\n*   The software development policy describes key requirements on acceptance of code commits & testing in chapter 2 as well as security principles in chapter 3.\n    \n*   Adjust based on your existing requirements if needed.",
